  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 0.54,
      "text": "English"
    },
    {
      "start": 0.54,
      "end": 21.19,
      "text": "다막 없이 영화를 볼 수 있는 그날까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.19,
      "end": 22.75,
      "text": "Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.75,
      "end": 25.09,
      "text": "11월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.09,
      "end": 29.69,
      "text": "Annette Benning, Sersha Ronan, Billy Howell, Gihane의"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.69,
      "end": 31.53,
      "text": "The Seagull, 갈매기"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.53,
      "end": 33.73,
      "text": "갈매기, 갈매기가 되겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.21,
      "end": 34.77,
      "text": "어서 오세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 35.13,
      "end": 35.45,
      "text": "Hello."
    },
    {
      "start": 35.79,
      "end": 36.41,
      "text": "Good to be here."
    },
    {
      "start": 36.49,
      "end": 37.17,
      "text": "Good morning, everyone."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.49,
      "end": 40.27,
      "text": "와, 제가, I've watched a video clip repeatedly"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.27,
      "end": 41.81,
      "text": "to deliver her name correctly."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.07,
      "end": 42.79,
      "text": "That name."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.83,
      "end": 43.09,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.25,
      "end": 44.55,
      "text": "That name is so hard to pronounce."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.81,
      "end": 45.75,
      "text": "진짜 미션이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 46.49,
      "end": 46.93,
      "text": "Sersha."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.89,
      "end": 48.37,
      "text": "Sersha."
    },
    {
      "start": 48.49,
      "end": 49.87,
      "text": "막 이러면서 연습 많이 했습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.21,
      "end": 52.37,
      "text": "S-A-O-I-R-S-E"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.37,
      "end": 53.55,
      "text": "Too many vowels."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.67,
      "end": 54.73,
      "text": "How is that Sersha?"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.73,
      "end": 58.05,
      "text": "She has a wonderful accent, by the way."
    },
    {
      "start": 58.13,
      "end": 59.67,
      "text": "I was watching her interviews."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.07,
      "end": 61.83,
      "text": "Very beautiful accent."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.97,
      "end": 63.01,
      "text": "Irish accent."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.25,
      "end": 65.41,
      "text": "그리고 목소리도 참 예뻐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.01,
      "end": 67.75,
      "text": "She should get into radio."
    },
    {
      "start": 68.05,
      "end": 68.65,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 68.79,
      "end": 70.97,
      "text": "Radio에도 참 잘 어울릴 목소리였습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.27,
      "end": 72.81,
      "text": "You should have her on the show."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.09,
      "end": 73.49,
      "text": "GMP."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.79,
      "end": 76.13,
      "text": "그러면 참 오늘일 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.47,
      "end": 77.55,
      "text": "If she visits Korea."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.61,
      "end": 77.83,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.37,
      "end": 78.93,
      "text": "One day."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.93,
      "end": 81.09,
      "text": "우리 크쌤하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.09,
      "end": 82.79,
      "text": "이제 또 니나가 만약에"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.79,
      "end": 84.05,
      "text": "직접 만나면 어떨까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.73,
      "end": 85.69,
      "text": "상상이 되어집니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.81,
      "end": 86.91,
      "text": "You should invite me and her."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.55,
      "end": 88.53,
      "text": "I was impressed."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.77,
      "end": 90.65,
      "text": "우리 그러면 배울 수 있겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.79,
      "end": 92.47,
      "text": "How to pronounce her name exactly."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.63,
      "end": 93.87,
      "text": "We can learn from her."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.97,
      "end": 95.27,
      "text": "The woman herself."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.49,
      "end": 95.81,
      "text": "우와."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.39,
      "end": 97.03,
      "text": "기대되네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.09,
      "end": 97.27,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.31,
      "end": 98.81,
      "text": "She teaches everybody who interviews me."
    },
    {
      "start": 98.93,
      "end": 99.83,
      "text": "Anyway, Sersha."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.95,
      "end": 100.11,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.15,
      "end": 101.31,
      "text": "한번 상상을 해봤습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.69,
      "end": 102.85,
      "text": "I hope to see Sersha one day."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.41,
      "end": 104.01,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.25,
      "end": 106.61,
      "text": "이 니나의 역할을 맡은 Sersha Ronan"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.61,
      "end": 109.63,
      "text": "그리고 Constantine 역할을 맡은 배우의 이름은"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.63,
      "end": 111.45,
      "text": "Billy Howell이라는 배우거든요."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.97,
      "end": 114.07,
      "text": "They've already known each other before."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.07,
      "end": 114.71,
      "text": "They did."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.81,
      "end": 116.15,
      "text": "They actually acted together"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.15,
      "end": 117.31,
      "text": "in another movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.31,
      "end": 120.05,
      "text": "and they were also love interests."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.29,
      "end": 121.65,
      "text": "아, 그랬군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.95,
      "end": 122.21,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.31,
      "end": 123.37,
      "text": "On Chesul Beach."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.45,
      "end": 123.87,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.93,
      "end": 125.15,
      "text": "It's a British movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.15,
      "end": 128.07,
      "text": "and they actually got married"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.07,
      "end": 130.35,
      "text": "and during their honeymoon"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.35,
      "end": 132.01,
      "text": "they broke up."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.63,
      "end": 133.51,
      "text": "Very tragic."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.53,
      "end": 134.31,
      "text": "It's not a happy ending."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.53,
      "end": 135.19,
      "text": "Not happy."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.37,
      "end": 136.91,
      "text": "They broke up and lived separately"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.91,
      "end": 137.85,
      "text": "for years and years"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.85,
      "end": 139.87,
      "text": "and then they saw each other"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.87,
      "end": 140.63,
      "text": "at the end of the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.63,
      "end": 142.75,
      "text": "but they were living separate lives."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.41,
      "end": 143.89,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.89,
      "end": 145.61,
      "text": "They just couldn't understand each other."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.13,
      "end": 146.75,
      "text": "They were very..."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.75,
      "end": 147.69,
      "text": "It was a very sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.69,
      "end": 148.91,
      "text": "kind of depressing movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.91,
      "end": 149.11,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.33,
      "end": 150.71,
      "text": "이 결혼 생활이라는 것이"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.71,
      "end": 152.95,
      "text": "requires constant efforts"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.95,
      "end": 153.63,
      "text": "from each other."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.73,
      "end": 154.17,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.35,
      "end": 156.31,
      "text": "Constant effort, sacrifice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.67,
      "end": 157.29,
      "text": "devotion."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.69,
      "end": 159.39,
      "text": "We have to recognize each other."
    },
    {
      "start": 159.75,
      "end": 159.87,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.23,
      "end": 160.39,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.39,
      "end": 162.03,
      "text": "서로를 서로에게"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.03,
      "end": 163.55,
      "text": "이제 인정을 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.55,
      "end": 164.49,
      "text": "인정을 시키고"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.49,
      "end": 165.41,
      "text": "이러는 과정들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.41,
      "end": 166.61,
      "text": "참 필요합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 166.95,
      "end": 167.09,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 167.09,
      "end": 168.21,
      "text": "못된 부분 조금 이렇게"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.21,
      "end": 168.89,
      "text": "등 돌리고."
    },
    {
      "start": 168.97,
      "end": 169.45,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.51,
      "end": 170.23,
      "text": "그럴 수도 있다."
    },
    {
      "start": 170.31,
      "end": 170.81,
      "text": "어, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 170.83,
      "end": 171.49,
      "text": "그럴 수 있어."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.55,
      "end": 172.85,
      "text": "뭐 내가 완벽하지 않은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.85,
      "end": 174.63,
      "text": "상대가 어떻게 완벽하길 바라겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.37,
      "end": 176.43,
      "text": "바로 그 말이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.45,
      "end": 176.95,
      "text": "그 말이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.13,
      "end": 178.57,
      "text": "아, 무슨 상담 받는 느낌."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.63,
      "end": 178.87,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.17,
      "end": 181.59,
      "text": "아, 그리고 we need patience too."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.79,
      "end": 181.97,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.41,
      "end": 183.85,
      "text": "Anyway, in this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.85,
      "end": 184.55,
      "text": "On Chesul Beach"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.55,
      "end": 186.63,
      "text": "their love was not successful."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.07,
      "end": 188.59,
      "text": "Also in The Seagull"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.59,
      "end": 190.69,
      "text": "they didn't end up together."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.77,
      "end": 191.23,
      "text": "그러네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 191.45,
      "end": 192.15,
      "text": "Yeah, hopefully maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.15,
      "end": 193.11,
      "text": "if they make another movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.11,
      "end": 193.85,
      "text": "together one day."
    },
    {
      "start": 193.91,
      "end": 194.75,
      "text": "A third movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 195.19,
      "end": 195.61,
      "text": "Finally!"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.83,
      "end": 197.41,
      "text": "Their love will blossom."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.69,
      "end": 198.47,
      "text": "I hope so."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.51,
      "end": 199.97,
      "text": "They will live happily ever after."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.97,
      "end": 202.17,
      "text": "아, 정말 해피 엔딩으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.17,
      "end": 203.11,
      "text": "끝나는 영화"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.11,
      "end": 204.05,
      "text": "이 둘이 한 번"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.05,
      "end": 204.79,
      "text": "촬영을 한 번 더"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.79,
      "end": 205.73,
      "text": "했으면 좋겠다라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.73,
      "end": 206.65,
      "text": "생각이 듭니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.15,
      "end": 208.29,
      "text": "네, 오늘 준비된 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.29,
      "end": 208.97,
      "text": "들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.91,
      "end": 210.75,
      "text": "Which of us looks younger?"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.15,
      "end": 212.07,
      "text": "You do, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.59,
      "end": 214.25,
      "text": "Ah, there, you see?"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.39,
      "end": 214.93,
      "text": "And why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.55,
      "end": 216.59,
      "text": "Because I work."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.69,
      "end": 217.99,
      "text": "I'm constantly doing something."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.59,
      "end": 219.57,
      "text": "I experience life."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.01,
      "end": 221.53,
      "text": "You just sit still in one place"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.53,
      "end": 222.51,
      "text": "not really living."
    },
    {
      "start": 223.15,
      "end": 223.45,
      "text": "Yes?"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.09,
      "end": 225.19,
      "text": "And I have a rule."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.85,
      "end": 227.65,
      "text": "I never think about the future."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.83,
      "end": 229.07,
      "text": "I never think about"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.07,
      "end": 229.97,
      "text": "old age or death."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.37,
      "end": 231.71,
      "text": "What will come in life will come."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.71,
      "end": 234.32,
      "text": "오, 이리나의 목소리가"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.32,
      "end": 235.32,
      "text": "많이 들렸는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.32,
      "end": 237.44,
      "text": "She didn't understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.44,
      "end": 238.62,
      "text": "Masha at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 238.86,
      "end": 239.14,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.26,
      "end": 239.44,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.44,
      "end": 241.58,
      "text": "Yeah, but I couldn't understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.58,
      "end": 242.2,
      "text": "이리나."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.7,
      "end": 243.26,
      "text": "Oh, really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.42,
      "end": 243.74,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.0,
      "end": 244.7,
      "text": "All the characters"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.7,
      "end": 245.86,
      "text": "are hard to understand."
    },
    {
      "start": 245.88,
      "end": 247.46,
      "text": "정말 어려운 캐릭터들인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.46,
      "end": 249.7,
      "text": "일단은 이리나의 캐릭터에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.7,
      "end": 251.48,
      "text": "디테일하게 알아볼 수"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.48,
      "end": 252.54,
      "text": "있었던 대화였습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 252.92,
      "end": 253.86,
      "text": "Yeah, she's talking about"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.86,
      "end": 255.06,
      "text": "her life philosophy."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.24,
      "end": 256.82,
      "text": "What comes will come."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.82,
      "end": 258.92,
      "text": "아, 인생 철학에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.92,
      "end": 259.9,
      "text": "이야기를 했었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 259.98,
      "end": 260.9,
      "text": "We can't help it."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.0,
      "end": 261.24,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.88,
      "end": 262.84,
      "text": "이리나하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.84,
      "end": 263.74,
      "text": "마샤의"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.74,
      "end": 265.1,
      "text": "이 인생 철학은"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.1,
      "end": 265.42,
      "text": "너무"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.42,
      "end": 266.58,
      "text": "They're too different."
    },
    {
      "start": 267.02,
      "end": 268.8,
      "text": "They're on opposite ends"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.8,
      "end": 269.52,
      "text": "of the spectrum."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.64,
      "end": 269.98,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 270.1,
      "end": 271.04,
      "text": "Polar opposites."
    },
    {
      "start": 271.12,
      "end": 272.36,
      "text": "극과 극이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.0,
      "end": 274.8,
      "text": "표현들 먼저 살펴보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.66,
      "end": 275.82,
      "text": "Constantly."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.82,
      "end": 276.54,
      "text": "Constantly."
    },
    {
      "start": 276.72,
      "end": 278.4,
      "text": "아, Constantine이 아니고"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.4,
      "end": 279.8,
      "text": "Constantly"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.8,
      "end": 280.88,
      "text": "라는 부사였어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 280.88,
      "end": 281.64,
      "text": "Constantly."
    },
    {
      "start": 281.64,
      "end": 283.04,
      "text": "네, 그래서"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.04,
      "end": 286.54,
      "text": "C-O-N-S-T-A-N-T-L-Y"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.54,
      "end": 287.6,
      "text": "지속적으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.6,
      "end": 288.46,
      "text": "계속해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.46,
      "end": 289.42,
      "text": "라는 부사입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 289.72,
      "end": 290.64,
      "text": "He keeps complaining."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.92,
      "end": 292.08,
      "text": "He constantly"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.08,
      "end": 293.38,
      "text": "complains."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.48,
      "end": 294.7,
      "text": "All the time."
    },
    {
      "start": 296.14,
      "end": 296.7,
      "text": "Sit still"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.7,
      "end": 297.82,
      "text": "in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.08,
      "end": 299.12,
      "text": "Sit still"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.12,
      "end": 299.8,
      "text": "이라고 있으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.8,
      "end": 301.46,
      "text": "가만히 앉다"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.46,
      "end": 302.06,
      "text": "라는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.38,
      "end": 303.54,
      "text": "In one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.76,
      "end": 304.4,
      "text": "한 곳에"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.4,
      "end": 305.64,
      "text": "가만히 앉다."
    },
    {
      "start": 306.08,
      "end": 306.72,
      "text": "Yeah, you say this"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.72,
      "end": 307.86,
      "text": "to your young kids a lot."
    },
    {
      "start": 307.86,
      "end": 308.26,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.7,
      "end": 309.44,
      "text": "Your young kids"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.44,
      "end": 310.54,
      "text": "who cannot sit still"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.54,
      "end": 311.24,
      "text": "in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.24,
      "end": 312.74,
      "text": "Sit still in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 312.78,
      "end": 313.6,
      "text": "아, 좀 가만히"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.6,
      "end": 314.3,
      "text": "좀 앉아 있어"
    },
    {
      "start": 314.3,
      "end": 315.24,
      "text": "라고 할 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.24,
      "end": 315.8,
      "text": "제발"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.8,
      "end": 317.02,
      "text": "Come on, please"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.02,
      "end": 318.06,
      "text": "sit still in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.12,
      "end": 318.36,
      "text": "아, 이"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.36,
      "end": 319.5,
      "text": "클리스쌤의 경험담에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.5,
      "end": 320.88,
      "text": "우러나오는 조언이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 320.98,
      "end": 321.26,
      "text": "Sit still."
    },
    {
      "start": 321.26,
      "end": 322.52,
      "text": "Especially in public places."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.12,
      "end": 323.64,
      "text": "Restaurants."
    },
    {
      "start": 324.16,
      "end": 325.24,
      "text": "Yeah, where you need"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.24,
      "end": 325.8,
      "text": "to sit still."
    },
    {
      "start": 325.96,
      "end": 326.28,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 326.46,
      "end": 327.52,
      "text": "Or you'll make a scene"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.52,
      "end": 328.66,
      "text": "and people will"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.66,
      "end": 330.18,
      "text": "눈치 막 줘요."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.48,
      "end": 331.12,
      "text": "그럴 때."
    },
    {
      "start": 331.5,
      "end": 332.1,
      "text": "그렇군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 333.5,
      "end": 334.96,
      "text": "What will come in life"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.96,
      "end": 335.7,
      "text": "will come."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.16,
      "end": 337.38,
      "text": "What will come"
    },
    {
      "start": 337.38,
      "end": 338.1,
      "text": "in life"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.1,
      "end": 338.82,
      "text": "will come."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.9,
      "end": 339.78,
      "text": "This is her life"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.78,
      "end": 340.34,
      "text": "philosophy."
    },
    {
      "start": 340.34,
      "end": 341.8,
      "text": "Yeah, 인생에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.8,
      "end": 342.64,
      "text": "올 것은"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.64,
      "end": 343.9,
      "text": "오고야만다."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.3,
      "end": 345.1,
      "text": "아, 인생에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.1,
      "end": 345.74,
      "text": "올 것은"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.74,
      "end": 347.06,
      "text": "다 오게 되어 있다"
    },
    {
      "start": 347.06,
      "end": 348.26,
      "text": "라는 해석입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 348.64,
      "end": 349.98,
      "text": "So, just relax."
    },
    {
      "start": 350.32,
      "end": 350.96,
      "text": "올 건 오니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.18,
      "end": 352.26,
      "text": "인생 철학이"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.26,
      "end": 352.78,
      "text": "어떤지"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.78,
      "end": 353.2,
      "text": "살짝"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.2,
      "end": 354.28,
      "text": "엿볼 수가 있었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.7,
      "end": 354.86,
      "text": "그리고"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.86,
      "end": 356.32,
      "text": "She's full of self-love."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.88,
      "end": 357.96,
      "text": "자기 애가"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.96,
      "end": 358.6,
      "text": "아주 넘치는"
    },
    {
      "start": 358.6,
      "end": 359.34,
      "text": "분인 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 359.74,
      "end": 360.62,
      "text": "She seems full of"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.62,
      "end": 361.64,
      "text": "love for herself."
    },
    {
      "start": 361.68,
      "end": 362.28,
      "text": "Yeah, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 362.4,
      "end": 362.96,
      "text": "Confidence."
    },
    {
      "start": 362.96,
      "end": 364.72,
      "text": "자, 다시 한 번"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.72,
      "end": 365.56,
      "text": "점검해 볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 366.42,
      "end": 367.3,
      "text": "Which of us looks younger?"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.7,
      "end": 368.64,
      "text": "You do, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 369.16,
      "end": 370.2,
      "text": "Ah, there."
    },
    {
      "start": 370.32,
      "end": 370.8,
      "text": "You see?"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.98,
      "end": 371.48,
      "text": "And why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 372.12,
      "end": 373.14,
      "text": "Because I work."
    },
    {
      "start": 373.24,
      "end": 374.54,
      "text": "I'm constantly doing something."
    },
    {
      "start": 375.1,
      "end": 376.12,
      "text": "I experience life."
    },
    {
      "start": 376.54,
      "end": 377.44,
      "text": "You just sit still"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.44,
      "end": 378.08,
      "text": "in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.16,
      "end": 379.08,
      "text": "Not really living."
    },
    {
      "start": 379.74,
      "end": 380.0,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 380.66,
      "end": 381.76,
      "text": "And I have a rule."
    },
    {
      "start": 382.42,
      "end": 384.22,
      "text": "I never think about the future."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.42,
      "end": 385.62,
      "text": "I never think about"
    },
    {
      "start": 385.62,
      "end": 386.52,
      "text": "old age or death."
    },
    {
      "start": 386.94,
      "end": 387.78,
      "text": "What will come in life"
    },
    {
      "start": 387.78,
      "end": 388.26,
      "text": "will come."
    },
    {
      "start": 388.26,
      "end": 390.89,
      "text": "네, 이리나와"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.89,
      "end": 392.13,
      "text": "도린 박사와"
    },
    {
      "start": 392.13,
      "end": 393.37,
      "text": "그리고 마샤"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.37,
      "end": 393.91,
      "text": "이렇게"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.91,
      "end": 395.05,
      "text": "세 명이"
    },
    {
      "start": 395.05,
      "end": 396.11,
      "text": "살짝살짝"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.11,
      "end": 397.09,
      "text": "아, 마샤까지는"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.09,
      "end": 397.65,
      "text": "아니었군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 397.99,
      "end": 398.27,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 398.27,
      "end": 399.83,
      "text": "세 명이 있는 장소에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.83,
      "end": 400.53,
      "text": "이리나와"
    },
    {
      "start": 400.53,
      "end": 402.03,
      "text": "도린의 대화였는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.03,
      "end": 403.69,
      "text": "이 도린 박사는"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.69,
      "end": 404.17,
      "text": "역시나"
    },
    {
      "start": 404.17,
      "end": 405.03,
      "text": "I was very gentle"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.03,
      "end": 405.71,
      "text": "and wise"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.71,
      "end": 406.19,
      "text": "했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 406.53,
      "end": 408.07,
      "text": "A very wise answer."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.19,
      "end": 408.45,
      "text": "왜냐하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 408.45,
      "end": 409.61,
      "text": "딱 봐도"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.61,
      "end": 410.09,
      "text": "마샤가"
    },
    {
      "start": 410.09,
      "end": 410.87,
      "text": "어려보였잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.23,
      "end": 411.45,
      "text": "아,"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.07,
      "end": 412.71,
      "text": "근데 이 주문"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.71,
      "end": 413.23,
      "text": "해도 되나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 413.59,
      "end": 414.45,
      "text": "그러게 말이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.67,
      "end": 415.75,
      "text": "Do you ask this question"
    },
    {
      "start": 415.75,
      "end": 416.65,
      "text": "to other people?"
    },
    {
      "start": 416.75,
      "end": 417.47,
      "text": "Never, never, never."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.47,
      "end": 418.41,
      "text": "If I'm with"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.41,
      "end": 419.35,
      "text": "if you're with your friend"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.35,
      "end": 420.75,
      "text": "Hey, which one of us"
    },
    {
      "start": 420.75,
      "end": 421.43,
      "text": "looks younger?"
    },
    {
      "start": 421.59,
      "end": 422.53,
      "text": "이거 뭔가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.61,
      "end": 423.35,
      "text": "그냥 이런 거 아니에요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 423.49,
      "end": 424.25,
      "text": "Mirror, mirror"
    },
    {
      "start": 424.25,
      "end": 425.03,
      "text": "on the wall."
    },
    {
      "start": 426.15,
      "end": 427.39,
      "text": "Who's the fairies"
    },
    {
      "start": 427.39,
      "end": 428.23,
      "text": "of them all?"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.39,
      "end": 428.93,
      "text": "이거하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.93,
      "end": 429.99,
      "text": "같은 맥락인 건가"
    },
    {
      "start": 429.99,
      "end": 430.41,
      "text": "싶어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 430.61,
      "end": 431.33,
      "text": "She's trying to"
    },
    {
      "start": 431.33,
      "end": 432.25,
      "text": "feed her ego."
    },
    {
      "start": 432.41,
      "end": 433.25,
      "text": "Tell me."
    },
    {
      "start": 433.95,
      "end": 434.49,
      "text": "공주병에"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.49,
      "end": 435.43,
      "text": "계속 있는 상황이"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.43,
      "end": 435.79,
      "text": "아닐까요,"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.89,
      "end": 436.37,
      "text": "이리나는?"
    },
    {
      "start": 436.49,
      "end": 437.09,
      "text": "바로 그거"
    },
    {
      "start": 437.09,
      "end": 437.39,
      "text": "온 거 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 437.41,
      "end": 437.67,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.01,
      "end": 438.33,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 438.47,
      "end": 439.47,
      "text": "자, 이리나의 질문"
    },
    {
      "start": 439.47,
      "end": 440.01,
      "text": "들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 440.85,
      "end": 441.55,
      "text": "Which of us"
    },
    {
      "start": 441.55,
      "end": 442.15,
      "text": "looks younger?"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.15,
      "end": 443.89,
      "text": "자, 옆에 있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.89,
      "end": 444.67,
      "text": "마샤와"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.67,
      "end": 445.47,
      "text": "자신을"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.47,
      "end": 446.31,
      "text": "이렇게 가리키면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.31,
      "end": 447.63,
      "text": "Dorne 박사에게"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.63,
      "end": 448.27,
      "text": "질문한 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.47,
      "end": 449.35,
      "text": "Which of us"
    },
    {
      "start": 449.35,
      "end": 450.19,
      "text": "looks younger?"
    },
    {
      "start": 450.87,
      "end": 451.29,
      "text": "누가 더"
    },
    {
      "start": 451.29,
      "end": 451.93,
      "text": "어려보여요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.05,
      "end": 452.63,
      "text": "Excuse me."
    },
    {
      "start": 452.69,
      "end": 453.47,
      "text": "Take a look at us."
    },
    {
      "start": 453.65,
      "end": 454.41,
      "text": "Take a look,"
    },
    {
      "start": 454.43,
      "end": 455.09,
      "text": "a close look."
    },
    {
      "start": 455.37,
      "end": 456.33,
      "text": "Which one of us"
    },
    {
      "start": 456.33,
      "end": 456.91,
      "text": "looks younger?"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.27,
      "end": 459.47,
      "text": "You do, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 460.19,
      "end": 460.89,
      "text": "Dorne 박사가"
    },
    {
      "start": 460.89,
      "end": 462.51,
      "text": "당연히 당신이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 462.85,
      "end": 463.87,
      "text": "라고 대답을 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 464.03,
      "end": 465.25,
      "text": "영혼 없는 대답이었어요,"
    },
    {
      "start": 465.31,
      "end": 465.59,
      "text": "아마도."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.81,
      "end": 467.11,
      "text": "Ah, a stupid question."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.17,
      "end": 468.17,
      "text": "A wise answer."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.69,
      "end": 469.61,
      "text": "You do, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 469.61,
      "end": 471.9,
      "text": "There, you see?"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.42,
      "end": 473.24,
      "text": "자랑하는 거야?"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.34,
      "end": 473.6,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 474.28,
      "end": 475.38,
      "text": "And why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.06,
      "end": 477.1,
      "text": "Because I work."
    },
    {
      "start": 477.22,
      "end": 478.1,
      "text": "네, there."
    },
    {
      "start": 478.26,
      "end": 478.68,
      "text": "You see?"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.96,
      "end": 479.66,
      "text": "그러면서 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.66,
      "end": 480.28,
      "text": "마샤에게"
    },
    {
      "start": 480.28,
      "end": 481.8,
      "text": "그치, 받지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.04,
      "end": 482.54,
      "text": "And why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.74,
      "end": 483.14,
      "text": "왠지 알아?"
    },
    {
      "start": 483.42,
      "end": 484.68,
      "text": "Because I work."
    },
    {
      "start": 485.04,
      "end": 486.36,
      "text": "나는 일을 하기 때문이야."
    },
    {
      "start": 486.42,
      "end": 486.94,
      "text": "어머, 어머, 어머."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.04,
      "end": 488.78,
      "text": "She's really rubbing salt"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.78,
      "end": 489.66,
      "text": "in the wound."
    },
    {
      "start": 489.8,
      "end": 490.16,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 490.16,
      "end": 491.32,
      "text": "She is really"
    },
    {
      "start": 491.32,
      "end": 492.72,
      "text": "just playing with"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.72,
      "end": 493.34,
      "text": "마샤."
    },
    {
      "start": 493.46,
      "end": 494.12,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 494.12,
      "end": 497.24,
      "text": "I'm constantly doing something."
    },
    {
      "start": 497.54,
      "end": 499.88,
      "text": "나는 constantly doing something."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.26,
      "end": 502.36,
      "text": "뭔가를 계속해서 하고 있어."
    },
    {
      "start": 502.82,
      "end": 504.06,
      "text": "I experience life."
    },
    {
      "start": 504.16,
      "end": 505.62,
      "text": "나는 삶을 경험하지."
    },
    {
      "start": 506.59,
      "end": 508.69,
      "text": "You just sit still in one place,"
    },
    {
      "start": 508.97,
      "end": 510.21,
      "text": "not really living."
    },
    {
      "start": 510.55,
      "end": 510.99,
      "text": "Yes?"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.29,
      "end": 513.67,
      "text": "You just sit still in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 513.67,
      "end": 515.19,
      "text": "이 장면에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 515.19,
      "end": 518.19,
      "text": "마샤는 옆에서 뜨개질 같은 것을 하고 있었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 518.31,
      "end": 519.05,
      "text": "Ah, she's knitting."
    },
    {
      "start": 519.45,
      "end": 519.97,
      "text": "네, 그래서"
    },
    {
      "start": 519.97,
      "end": 522.21,
      "text": "You just sit still in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 522.21,
      "end": 525.03,
      "text": "너는 그냥 한 곳에서 가만히 앉아 있어."
    },
    {
      "start": 525.33,
      "end": 526.35,
      "text": "Not really living"
    },
    {
      "start": 526.35,
      "end": 526.93,
      "text": "이라고 했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 526.93,
      "end": 527.77,
      "text": "이것은"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.77,
      "end": 529.89,
      "text": "And you are not really living"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.89,
      "end": 531.45,
      "text": "이거하고 같은 의미가 되겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 532.09,
      "end": 533.21,
      "text": "사는 게 아니잖아"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.21,
      "end": 534.09,
      "text": "라는 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 535.09,
      "end": 536.31,
      "text": "You don't live life."
    },
    {
      "start": 536.49,
      "end": 537.85,
      "text": "You just sit still"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.85,
      "end": 539.11,
      "text": "and do nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 539.53,
      "end": 540.33,
      "text": "Look at me."
    },
    {
      "start": 540.83,
      "end": 541.03,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.45,
      "end": 542.57,
      "text": "Why is she doing this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.91,
      "end": 543.45,
      "text": "그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 543.51,
      "end": 544.57,
      "text": "너무 비교하는 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 544.87,
      "end": 545.55,
      "text": "잘났네."
    },
    {
      "start": 545.69,
      "end": 547.53,
      "text": "네, 잘난 척 엄청 하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 548.61,
      "end": 549.63,
      "text": "And I have a rule."
    },
    {
      "start": 550.01,
      "end": 551.15,
      "text": "나는 규칙이 있지."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.3,
      "end": 553.92,
      "text": "I never think about the future."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.64,
      "end": 557.0,
      "text": "나는 결코 미래에 대해서 생각하지 않아."
    },
    {
      "start": 557.26,
      "end": 558.76,
      "text": "I never think about the future."
    },
    {
      "start": 559.44,
      "end": 562.18,
      "text": "I never think about old age or death."
    },
    {
      "start": 562.32,
      "end": 562.86,
      "text": "그리고"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.86,
      "end": 565.3,
      "text": "I never think about old age."
    },
    {
      "start": 566.64,
      "end": 567.28,
      "text": "노년이라든지"
    },
    {
      "start": 567.28,
      "end": 568.12,
      "text": "or death."
    },
    {
      "start": 568.44,
      "end": 570.6,
      "text": "죽음에 대해서도 절대 생각하지 않아."
    },
    {
      "start": 571.34,
      "end": 573.22,
      "text": "What will come in life will come."
    },
    {
      "start": 573.22,
      "end": 575.88,
      "text": "음, 인생 철학을 마지막에 이야기해주네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 576.4,
      "end": 579.84,
      "text": "살면서 다가오는 건 어차피 다 오게 되어 있어"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.84,
      "end": 581.64,
      "text": "라는 이야기입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 581.64,
      "end": 583.64,
      "text": "한편으로는"
    },
    {
      "start": 583.64,
      "end": 586.16,
      "text": "이리나가 was a simple-minded person"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.16,
      "end": 586.7,
      "text": "인 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 586.92,
      "end": 587.26,
      "text": "아하."
    },
    {
      "start": 587.38,
      "end": 587.68,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 587.78,
      "end": 588.4,
      "text": "좋게 보면."
    },
    {
      "start": 588.64,
      "end": 589.34,
      "text": "좋게 보면."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.46,
      "end": 590.98,
      "text": "단순한 생각을 하고 사는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.98,
      "end": 592.86,
      "text": "본인에게는 건강에도 좋을 수 있으니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.2,
      "end": 593.3,
      "text": "아."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.48,
      "end": 593.64,
      "text": "예."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.64,
      "end": 595.32,
      "text": "근데 이제 남에 대한 배려가"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.32,
      "end": 597.2,
      "text": "너무 없다라는 생각이 듭니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 597.38,
      "end": 597.82,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 598.06,
      "end": 600.06,
      "text": "She is getting out of line."
    },
    {
      "start": 600.16,
      "end": 600.44,
      "text": "예."
    },
    {
      "start": 600.68,
      "end": 601.04,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 601.04,
      "end": 604.2,
      "text": "자, 이 장면 마지막으로 한 번 더 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 604.2,
      "end": 605.76,
      "text": "Which of us looks younger?"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.12,
      "end": 607.06,
      "text": "You do, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 607.6,
      "end": 607.86,
      "text": "Ah."
    },
    {
      "start": 608.22,
      "end": 608.62,
      "text": "There."
    },
    {
      "start": 608.72,
      "end": 609.24,
      "text": "You see?"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.42,
      "end": 609.92,
      "text": "And why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.56,
      "end": 611.58,
      "text": "Because I work."
    },
    {
      "start": 611.68,
      "end": 612.96,
      "text": "I'm constantly doing something."
    },
    {
      "start": 613.56,
      "end": 614.56,
      "text": "I experience life."
    },
    {
      "start": 615.0,
      "end": 616.52,
      "text": "You just sit still in one place."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.6,
      "end": 617.5,
      "text": "Not really living."
    },
    {
      "start": 618.16,
      "end": 618.44,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 619.0,
      "end": 620.2,
      "text": "And I have a rule."
    },
    {
      "start": 620.84,
      "end": 622.66,
      "text": "I never think about the future."
    },
    {
      "start": 622.82,
      "end": 624.98,
      "text": "I never think about old age or death."
    },
    {
      "start": 624.98,
      "end": 626.7,
      "text": "What will come in life will come."
    },
    {
      "start": 627.85,
      "end": 627.99,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 628.45,
      "end": 629.85,
      "text": "아모르 님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.85,
      "end": 631.85,
      "text": "크쌤 너무 웃겨요."
    },
    {
      "start": 632.11,
      "end": 632.51,
      "text": "Bye."
    },
    {
      "start": 632.79,
      "end": 634.19,
      "text": "See you next Monday."
    }
  ]
}